@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Flight Control Operator" as FCO
participant ":System" as System
participant ":Report Generation Thread" as ReportThread
participant ":Simulation Data" as SimulationData
participant ":Simulation Report" as Report
participant ":Report File" as ReportFile

activate FCO

FCO -> System : Requests simulation report

activate System
System --> System : Check if FCO is authenticated and authorized
System --> System : Validate selected simulation

alt simulation exists

    System -> ReportThread : Request simulation report summary

    activate ReportThread

    ReportThread -> SimulationData : Read total number of flights
    activate SimulationData
    SimulationData --> ReportThread : Total number of flights
    deactivate SimulationData

    ReportThread -> SimulationData : Read flight execution statuses
    activate SimulationData
    SimulationData --> ReportThread : Execution statuses
    deactivate SimulationData

    ReportThread -> SimulationData : Read safety violation timestamps and positions
    activate SimulationData
    SimulationData --> ReportThread : Safety violation data
    deactivate SimulationData

    ReportThread -> SimulationData : Read pass/fail validation result
    activate SimulationData
    SimulationData --> ReportThread : Validation result
    deactivate SimulationData

    ReportThread -> Report : Compile simulation summary report
    activate Report
    Report --> ReportThread : Report compiled
    deactivate Report

    ReportThread -> ReportFile : Store report in file
    activate ReportFile
    ReportFile --> ReportThread : Report file saved
    deactivate ReportFile

    ReportThread --> System : Report file reference
    deactivate ReportThread

    System --> FCO : Display simulation report summary

else simulation does not exist

    System --> FCO : Display simulation not found message

else report generation or storage fails

    System --> FCO : Display report generation/storage error

end

deactivate System
deactivate FCO

@enduml